                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4920" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0775</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9619 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇聚精英，开辟鸿蒙：汇鸿外经的网络嵌入性国际化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gathering the elite, Opening a new world: The chain-Embedding Int’l Road of High Hope Skyrun Inc.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘雪梅，陈光烨，李金生，徐永祺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇鸿外经国际集团外经有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略；网络嵌入；全球价值链；资源双向流动；2020百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International Strategy; Chain Embedding; Global Value Chain; Two-way Flow of Resources</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对外贸企业来说，有效嵌入全球价值链是经营成功的重要条件。从2005年至今，汇鸿外经在尼日利亚深耕细作十五载，从单纯的配件组装发展到在当地制造生产，从单一的家电业务发展到家电、电力、可可三大产业并驾齐驱，公司的国际化之路取得了瞩目的成绩，促进了中尼两国的经济合作。本案例系统梳理了汇鸿外经的国际化发展历程，展现了其进军尼日利亚市场五个重要发展阶段的风险判断及应对措施，探讨中小企业在不同发展阶段的全球价值链嵌入问题。通过本案例的学习，学员可以掌握企业如何通过网络嵌入性国际化模式创新管理和提升收益，实现资源双向流动，促进国际化战略的顺利实施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">For a foreign trade incorporation, it is an important condition for successful management to embed in global value Chains effectively. The High Hope Skyrun incorporation has cultivated the Nigerian market for 15 years. Her business ranges from simple components assembly to local manufacturing, and from a single household appliance to three-parallel-industries: i.e. household appliances, electric power and cocoa. The international road of Skyrun Corporation has gained great achievements and made a tremendous contribution to the economic development of China and Nigeria. This case systematically summarizes the overseas developments of Skyrun Corporation, and presents its risk assessment and countermeasures during entering the Nigerian market at four key stages of development, and then discusses the problems of global value chain encountered in different development stages for small and medium-sized enterprises. Through the study of this case, the readers will understand how to innovate their managements and increase revenue with the international chain embedding mode for enterprises, consequently realize two-way flow of resources and promote successful implementation of the international strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《国际商务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化战略 全球资源筹供与价值链协调</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-11</td>
                            </tr>
